Recently, a video of "two traffic police teasing a woman" in a local group in Xiamen caused public dissatisfaction.
In the video, in the middle of the road, two traffic police threw the car keys of a woman riding an electric bike to each other during law enforcement, causing the woman to run back and forth. During this time, there were also vehicles passing by, which was very dangerous.
It is reported that because Xiamen is "building a civilized city" recently, the control of electric bikes is relatively strict.
